name: Vectra, The last mystery
description: 2000 years after every claimed monster was destroyed there was a complaint deep inside the neck of Cloud City one day where a DNA formed a Boss brain. Your mission is simple, kill all the electronic dolls and destroy the Brain to eliminate hell itself. The Level is set deep inside the neck of Cloud City where Luke took on Darth Vader in the pit 2045 years before. The Vectra is a floating platform which was installed in 2759AD and is a new device which powers Cloud City.
